name: edgeworker_eventhandler
sql:
(edgeworker_eventhandler) -> multiIf (
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '-',
  'No event handler was executed',
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '1',
  'onClientRequest',
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '2',
  'onOriginRequest',
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '3',
  'onOriginResponse',
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '4',
  'onClientResponse',
  edgeworker_eventhandler = '5',
  'responseProvider',
  edgeworker_eventhandler
)
